.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm ucard_errno
and
.Nm kiosk_errno
functions return the last error encountered by the provided
.Vt ucard
or
.Vt kiosk .
.Pp
The
.Nm libucard_strerror
function returns the error text corresponding to an error code, and the
.Nm libucard_strerror_r
fuction writes this message in the buffer
.Vt strbuf
of size
.Vt buflen .
.Pp
The
.Nm ucard_perror
and
.Nm kiosk_perror
function displays
.Vt message ,
followed by a colon, and the message corresponding to the last error
encountered by the
.Vt ucard
or
.Vt kiosk .

